metadata.description:
Spirit Shield, exactly what you need for your soul.. The only thing protecting us from the outer world and the inner world at once. A filtration system. A means to an end thats never ending.. One trains in the art of shielding, without blocking what is for us. 

I questioned putting this song on Presessence volume 1, so i wanted to drop It for the year anniversary! 

recorded in 2020 - released on an incredible album by Kato 

//// 

Produced by Kato, written and performed by Domino, mixed by Steeziak, Mastered by Dave
